## Vocative Changes (Collapsible)

<section expandable="true" default="collapsed">
<title>Vocative Changes (Direct Address)</title>

Masculine nouns change their ending for direct address:
- -ος → -ε (φίλος → φίλε!)
- -ας → -α (πατέρας → πατέρα!)
- -ης → -η (μαθητής → μαθητή!)
- -ές → -έ (καφές → καφέ!)

Feminine and neuter nouns keep nominative form.

</section>

